 &lt;td style="text-align: left">-&lt;/td>
 &lt;td style="text-align: left">96&lt;/td>
 &lt;td style="text-align: left">340 potency action that combos off of True Thrust/Raiden Thrust. Direct upgrade to Vorpal Thrust, replacing the original action.&lt;/td>
 &lt;/tr>
 &lt;tr>
 &lt;td style="text-align: left">
&lt;div class="md__image">
